data.description: Short Sale. Almost new construction! DR Horton Cali floor plan in the heart of SE Palm Coast.  Good schools, close to beach (15 minutes) and close to shopping. Jump on I95 to Daytona or St. Augustine in 10 minutes. Open concept main living area, primary bedroom with 2 closets and walk in shower and double sinks. 3 bedrooms, garage and laundry room at the front of this over 1800 square foot house.  Lots of room for play room or home school space.  Comes with garage door opener, gutters and irrigation system.  Private back yard with 6' vinyl fence.
